santa 's workshop is a disney short film directed by wilfred jackson , first released on december 10 , 1932 in the silly symphonies series . the film features santa claus and his elves preparing for christmas in santa 's workshop . a sequel , the night before christmas , partially based on a visit from st. nicholas , was made the year after , portraying santa leaving the toys in a house with nine children . in sweden and norway , santa 's workshop is part of the christmas television special from all of us to all of you , traditionally shown at christmas eve . various stereotypes in the film have been censored several times . the short features the first of the marche &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; by franz peter schubert .